00:28:52,800 --> 00:28:55,120
 dakle, non-stop konstantna pasivnost

1013
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:56,580
 te dovodi upravo

1014
00:28:56,580 --> 00:28:59,140
 do manjka kompetencija u srednjim godinama.

1015
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:00,840
 To je zapravo ono što je zadnje.

1016
00:29:00,840 --> 00:29:02,680
 Poglejamo sada Josipa u srednjim godinama.

1017
00:29:02,680 --> 00:29:03,860
 Dakle, vidimo,

1018
00:29:03,860 --> 00:29:06,940
 Josip sluša od anđela sve što je Isus.

1019
00:29:06,940 --> 00:29:07,620
 Je li tako?

1020
00:29:07,620 --> 00:29:08,940
 Mesija, ovo ono,

1021
00:29:08,940 --> 00:29:10,120
 Boži sin

1022
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:11,960
 i upravo u onoj gesti,

1023
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:13,360
 kada ga vodi u hram,

1024
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:14,040
 kada i ne treba,

1025
00:29:14,100 --> 00:29:16,580
 sjetite se kada sam na trećoj kateheziji obješljavao

1026
00:29:16,580 --> 00:29:18,240
 da je neobično da

1027
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:21,400
 muškarci su ti koji jedini idu u hram,

1028
00:29:21,400 --> 00:29:22,600
 a Josip sa sobom

1029
00:29:22,600 --> 00:29:24,540
 vuče i Mariju i Isusa,

1030
00:29:24,540 --> 00:29:26,020
 onda i kada ga nije trebao.

1031
00:29:26,020 --> 00:29:28,420
 Dakle, upravo u tome on pokazuje,

1032
00:29:28,420 --> 00:29:30,400
 dakle, ja sam slušao,

1033
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,480
 razumijem

1034
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:33,100
 tko je Isus

1035
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:34,440
 i što se ovdje događa

1036
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:36,440
 i onda i kada nije obavezan,

1037
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,320
 on, cijela sveta obitelj,

1038
00:29:38,320 --> 00:29:39,160
 ide u hram.

1039
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:41,420
 Dakle, i tu dolazimo

1040
00:29:41,420 --> 00:29:43,000
 do treće odlike,

1041
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:45,220
 ovo je to sam onako nazvao

1042
00:29:45,220 --> 00:29:46,220
 da zvuči profi,

1043
00:29:46,220 --> 00:29:48,640
 ali objasniću što mi to trebalo značiti.

1044
00:29:48,640 --> 00:29:50,460
 Dakle, iz te kompetencije

1045
00:29:50,460 --> 00:29:52,320
 dolazimo do integritet

1046
00:29:52,320 --> 00:29:53,440
 u trenutku izbora.

1047
00:29:53,440 --> 00:29:54,740
 Ovo mi je najdraži.

1048
00:29:54,740 --> 00:29:56,080
 A sad ćemo objasniti što to znači

1049
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:57,480
 integritet u trenutku izbora.

1050
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:57,700
 Ok.

1051
00:29:57,700 --> 00:29:59,880
 Dakle, vrlo jednostavno.

1052
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:02,640
 Dakle, integritet u trenutku izbora.

1053
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:04,400
 Dakle, znači prvo odgovoran,

1054
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:05,620
 drugo kompetentan

1055
00:30:05,620 --> 00:30:06,520
 i trećo slobodan.

1056
00:30:07,180 --> 00:30:07,920
 Slobodan muž,

1057
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:08,920
 slobodan muškarac.

1058
00:30:08,920 --> 00:30:10,600
 Rastavite se, šalim se, ne to.

1059
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:14,660
 Kako je muž slobodan u braku?

1060
00:30:14,660 --> 00:30:15,500
 Ne znam.

1061
00:30:15,500 --> 00:30:18,480
 Ok.

1062
00:30:18,480 --> 00:30:19,760
 Dobro.

1063
00:30:19,760 --> 00:30:21,240
 Ovako.

1064
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:24,020
 Naravno, mi imamo svoje obveze.

1065
00:30:24,020 --> 00:30:26,700
 Ja u sečeništvu,

1066
00:30:26,700 --> 00:30:27,620
 vi u braku,

1067
00:30:27,620 --> 00:30:28,600
 kao muževi i tako dalje.

1068
00:30:28,600 --> 00:30:29,240
 Postoje obveze,

1069
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,540
 postoje okviri u kojima jeste.

1070
00:30:30,540 --> 00:30:32,440
 Nažalost, to ste i zabrali

1071
00:30:32,440 --> 00:30:33,260
 i postoje okviri.

1072
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:33,880
 Ta ono,

1073
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,660
 ono dosadno,

1074
00:30:34,660 --> 00:30:35,640
 ne možeš izvan toga.

1075
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:37,500
 Međutim, kako biti slobodan

1076
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:39,500
 ne od svojih obveza,

1077
00:30:39,500 --> 00:30:40,880
 nego biti slobodan

1078
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:42,100
 u svojim obvezama?

1079
00:30:42,100 --> 00:30:43,580
 Pogledajte, znači,

1080
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:46,980
 učinite se slobodnim u stvarima

1081
00:30:46,980 --> 00:30:48,220
 koje moram učiniti.

1082
00:30:48,220 --> 00:30:49,680
 Dakle, biti doma,

1083
00:30:49,780 --> 00:30:52,540
 buditi se kada se mama ne može probuditi,

1084
00:30:52,540 --> 00:30:54,600
 odvesti kada mama ne može odvesti

1085
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:55,260
 ili tako dalje.

1086
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:57,660
 Znači, stvari koje se očekuju od mene

1087
00:30:57,660 --> 00:30:58,220
 kao od oca,

1088
00:30:58,220 --> 00:30:59,100
 kao od muškarca,

1089
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:00,780
 koje su moje obveze.

1090
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:01,860
 Jer, recimo, ja sam to nazvao

1091
00:31:01,860 --> 00:31:02,980
 onako herojska minuta.

1092
00:31:02,980 --> 00:31:04,740
 Što je herojska minuta?

1093
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:07,300
 Dakle, postoji svako jutro vrijeme

1094
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:09,100
 kada si naštimaš budelicu.

1095
00:31:09,100 --> 00:31:09,840
 To je tvoje vrijeme

1096
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:10,940
 kada se moraš buditi

1097
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:12,120
 da bi, ne znam,

1098
00:31:12,120 --> 00:31:13,600
 se spremio, tišao na posao

1099
00:31:13,600 --> 00:31:14,740
 ili neka treća obveza.

1100
00:31:14,740 --> 00:31:16,400
 Dakle, svako jutro postoji

1101
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:18,100
 ta molotona, jedna, te ista,

1102
00:31:18,100 --> 00:31:19,560
 ono, ne snuz,

1103
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:20,680
 ne ostav snuz,

1104
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,720
 nego baš to.

1105
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:23,240
 Herojska minuta je,

1106
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:24,280
 ja se moram,

1107
00:31:24,280 --> 00:31:26,260
 znati, ja se moram probuditi šest,

1108
00:31:26,260 --> 00:31:26,980
 svako jutro.

1109
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:27,660
 E, neću.

1110
00:31:27,660 --> 00:31:29,920
 Probudit ću se minutu prije.

1111
00:31:29,920 --> 00:31:32,400
 Neće mi budelica odrediti.

1112
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,880
 Ja sam slobodan odrediti

1113
00:31:33,880 --> 00:31:34,980
 kada ću se ja probuditi.

1114
00:31:35,520 --> 00:31:36,240
 Ili drugi primjer.

1115
00:31:36,240 --> 00:31:39,500
 Dakle, odlučujem,

1116
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:40,920
 ajmo reći,

1117
00:31:40,920 --> 00:31:42,300
 odlučujem za sebe

1118
00:31:42,300 --> 00:31:43,300
 kakav ću čovjek biti.

1119
00:31:43,300 --> 00:31:45,620
 Daću ovaj primjer iz evanđelja.

1120
00:31:45,620 --> 00:31:47,360
 To je nešto što vas sada čeka

1121
00:31:47,360 --> 00:31:48,060
 ovu nedjelju.

1122
00:31:48,060 --> 00:31:49,420
 Ovo je ulomak iz evanđelja

1123
00:31:49,420 --> 00:31:50,720
 o ljubav prema neprijateljima.

1124
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:53,560
 Mate 5.38-40

1125
00:31:53,560 --> 00:31:54,400
 kada Isus kaže

1126
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:55,640
 naprotiv,

1127
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,680
 pljusne li te tko

1128
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:57,720
 po desnom obrazu

1129
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,720
 okreni mu i drugi.

1130
00:31:58,720 --> 00:31:59,840
 Onomu tko bi se htio

1131
00:31:59,840 --> 00:32:00,720
 s tomo paničiti

1132
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,520
 da bi se domogao

1133
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:02,440
 tvoje donje haljine

1134
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,540
 prepusti i gornju.

1135
00:32:03,540 --> 00:32:05,000
 Ako te tko prisili

1136
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:05,700
 jednu milju

1137
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:06,820
 pođi s njim dvije.

1138
00:32:06,820 --> 00:32:08,280
 Što to zapravo znači?

1139
00:32:08,280 --> 00:32:09,460
 Kakva je to?

1140
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:11,600
 Isus ovdje želi reći

1141
00:32:11,600 --> 00:32:13,360
 neprijatelj

1142
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,640
 time što te udario

1143
00:32:14,640 --> 00:32:15,840
 time što je od tebe

1144
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:16,780
 nešto oteo

1145
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:18,280
 i time što te nagovorio

1146
00:32:18,280 --> 00:32:19,060
 odnosno prisilio

1147
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:20,000
 da moraš s njim šetat

1148
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:21,240
 on te zarobio

1149
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,760
 i ti kao da nisi slobodan.

1150
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:24,280
 Međutim Isus kaže

1151
00:32:24,280 --> 00:32:25,900
 ti i tada zarobljen

1152
00:32:25,900 --> 00:32:27,640
 možeš pokazati svoju slobodu.

1153
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,760
 Naprimjer

1154
00:32:28,760 --> 00:32:30,560
 moraš ići sa mnom

1155
00:32:30,560 --> 00:32:31,140
 jednu milju.

1156
00:32:31,140 --> 00:32:32,600
 Ok, ideš s njim jednu milju

1157
00:32:32,600 --> 00:32:33,860
 i nastaviš s njim medalje.

1158
00:32:33,860 --> 00:32:35,360
 Dobro, šta sad?

1159
00:32:35,360 --> 00:32:36,780
 Ovo sam sad ja izabrao.

1160
00:32:36,780 --> 00:32:38,700
 Ja sad idem s tobom.

1161
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:39,800
 Ti mi nisi zapovjedio

1162
00:32:39,800 --> 00:32:40,560
 da ti pokažu

1163
00:32:40,560 --> 00:32:41,400
 koliko sam slobodan.

1164
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,440
 Ili recimo

1165
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:43,800
 neko te pljuse po obrazu.

1166
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:44,940
 Dakle,

1167
00:32:44,940 --> 00:32:46,580
 ti kažeš

1168
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:46,940
 ok,

1169
00:32:46,940 --> 00:32:48,380
 evo ti i drugi.

1170
00:32:48,380 --> 00:32:49,940
 To je moja sloboda.

1171
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,400
 To je moja sloboda.

1172
00:32:51,400 --> 00:32:52,540
 Dakle,

1173
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:53,220
 ili recimo

1174
00:32:53,220 --> 00:32:55,240
 ko bi se htio s tobom parničiti

1175
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:55,880
 da bi se domogao

1176
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:56,700
 tvoje donje haljide

1177
00:32:56,700 --> 00:32:57,820
 prepusti i gornju.

1178
00:32:57,820 --> 00:32:58,240
 Dakle,

1179
00:32:58,240 --> 00:32:59,480
 neko ti je oteo nešto

1180
00:32:59,480 --> 00:33:00,000
 kaže

1181
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:00,860
 ok, uzmi i ovo.

1182
00:33:00,860 --> 00:33:01,820
 Ovo ti sad ja dajem me.

1183
00:33:01,820 --> 00:33:03,080
 Dakle,

1184
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:03,900
 tu pokazuješ

1185
00:33:03,900 --> 00:33:05,360
 kada te neko želi zarobiti

1186
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:06,200
 nekim zlom,

1187
00:33:06,200 --> 00:33:07,320
 svojim vlastitim zlom

1188
00:33:07,320 --> 00:33:08,880
 ti i dalje možeš se ponašati

1189
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:09,440
 slobodno,

1190
00:33:09,440 --> 00:33:10,540
 neuvjetovano.

1191
00:33:10,540 --> 00:33:11,780
 To je ono što Isus zapravo

1192
00:33:11,780 --> 00:33:13,180
 ovime ovdje želi reći.

1193
00:33:13,180 --> 00:33:13,920
 Pogotovo ovime

1194
00:33:13,920 --> 00:33:15,240
 ako ti je tko prisili

1195
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:15,660
 jednu milju,

1196
00:33:15,660 --> 00:33:16,400
 pođe s njim dvije.

1197
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:17,380
 To je baš iz rimskog

1198
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:18,660
 robovlasničkog sustava.

1199
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:19,400
 Dakle,

1200
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:21,140
 rob je morao

1201
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:22,140
 svaki dan

1202
00:33:22,140 --> 00:33:23,640
 bio je prisiljen

1203
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,580
 sa svojim vlasnikom

1204
00:33:24,580 --> 00:33:25,440
 proći jednu milju,

1205
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,460
 prošetati s njime.

1206
00:33:26,460 --> 00:33:27,200
 Obavezno.

1207
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,380
 Obavezno.

1208
00:33:28,380 --> 00:33:29,780
 I zato ovdje Isus kaže

1209
00:33:29,780 --> 00:33:31,420
 ovo je robovlasnički,

1210
00:33:31,420 --> 00:33:32,040
 jedna milja.

1211
00:33:32,040 --> 00:33:33,360
 Ti pođe s njim i dalje

1212
00:33:33,360 --> 00:33:34,240
 da mu pokažeš

1213
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,940
 da si slobodan.

1214
00:33:34,940 --> 00:33:36,360
 Da to je svoj slobodni izbor.

1215
00:33:36,360 --> 00:33:37,000
 Tako i ovdje.

1216
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:38,980
 Ultar nekih svojih izbora,

1217
00:33:38,980 --> 00:33:40,680
 ultar nekih svojih obveza

1218
00:33:40,680 --> 00:33:41,760
 kao muškarac, otac,

1219
00:33:41,760 --> 00:33:43,540
 recimo svečenik i tako dalje,

1220
00:33:43,540 --> 00:33:46,220
 ti možeš i dalje

1221
00:33:46,220 --> 00:33:47,380
 pokazati svoju slobodu.

1222
00:33:47,380 --> 00:33:50,000
 Dakle, žena ti kaže

1223
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,540
 daj se probudi

1224
00:33:51,540 --> 00:33:53,860
 ponudaj u tri ujutro

1225
00:33:53,860 --> 00:33:54,940
 ovo ono i tako dalje.

1226
00:33:54,940 --> 00:33:56,600
 Ok, ti to nekako

1227
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:59,360
 kao danas je tvoj red

1228
00:33:59,360 --> 00:34:00,520
 i to moraš večeras je tvoj red.

1229
00:34:00,520 --> 00:34:01,460
 Ne znam kako to funkcionira

1230
00:34:01,460 --> 00:34:02,240
 kod vas, ne dam pojma.

1231
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:05,960
 Dakle, da, dobro.

1232
00:34:05,960 --> 00:34:08,740
 E, i onda kažeš dobro, večeras

1233
00:34:08,740 --> 00:34:10,440
 i onda sutra opet to napraviš isto.

1234
00:34:10,440 --> 00:34:11,360
 Iako je njezin red.

1235
00:34:11,360 --> 00:34:14,240
 Ne, evo, ja sam to odlovio

1236
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:15,060
 sad moja sloboda.

1237
00:34:15,060 --> 00:34:16,740
 Nisem me uvjetovala,

1238
00:34:16,740 --> 00:34:17,340
 sam ću ja pokazati

1239
00:34:17,340 --> 00:34:18,600
 da ja to zaista

1240
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:20,140
 svojim izborom želim.

1241
00:34:20,140 --> 00:34:20,920
 U tom smislu.

1242
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:23,220
 Dakle, vidimo Josip je sloboda

1243
00:34:23,220 --> 00:34:24,700
 u trenutku bijega u Egipat.

1244
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:27,660
 Dakle, nje tu pokazuje svoje...

1245
00:34:27,660 --> 00:34:28,520
 Dakle, ne poziva se ono

1246
00:34:28,520 --> 00:34:30,360
 sjeti se na svoje kraljevsko pravo.

1247
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:32,340
 Znači, on zna da je njegova obitelj

1248
00:34:32,340 --> 00:34:32,900
 ugrožena,

1249
00:34:32,900 --> 00:34:35,120
 ovaj, da tako zaštiti svoju obitelj,

1250
00:34:35,120 --> 00:34:37,060
 da njego odlučuje ostati skrovit

1251
00:34:37,060 --> 00:34:38,100
 kao i do sada.

1252
00:34:38,100 --> 00:34:38,980
 Tu je njegova poniznost

1253
00:34:38,980 --> 00:34:40,720
 najviše zapravo, zapravo na testu.

1254
00:34:40,720 --> 00:34:41,900
 Da se ne vraćam na ono prvo

1255
00:34:41,900 --> 00:34:43,240
 kad sam umjašnjavao

1256
00:34:43,240 --> 00:34:45,460
 koje su bile Josipove mogućnosti

1257
00:34:45,460 --> 00:34:47,600
 kao kraljevske dinastije,

1258
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:50,640
 nasuprot Heroda lažnog kralja

1259
00:34:50,640 --> 00:34:52,020
 i tako dalje.

1260
00:34:52,020 --> 00:34:52,880
 Dobro da sad dajdemo to.

1261
00:34:53,600 --> 00:34:55,060
 I četvrto, zadnje,

1262
00:34:55,060 --> 00:34:56,800
 dakle, odlika,

1263
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:58,760
 znači, zapamtite,

1264
00:34:58,760 --> 00:34:59,760
 prvo, odgovoran,

1265
00:34:59,760 --> 00:35:01,220
 drugo, kompetentan,

1266
00:35:01,220 --> 00:35:03,040
 treće, biti slobodan,

1267
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,940
 znači, integritet u trenutku izbora.

1268
00:35:04,940 --> 00:35:06,560
 I četvrto,

1269
00:35:06,560 --> 00:35:07,960
 dakle, ja ću biti taj čovjek,

1270
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,020
 čovjek Heroske minute.

1271
00:35:09,020 --> 00:35:10,460
 To je to, biti slobodan.

1272
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,700
 Čovjek Heroske minute.

1273
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:14,320
 I četvrto, biti kompetitivan,

1274
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,260
 možemo to tako reći,

1275
00:35:15,260 --> 00:35:17,440
 odnosno natjecateljski raspoložen.

1276
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,340
 Ko je,

1277
00:35:18,340 --> 00:35:21,300
 muška odlika je da se dostupno tječeš,

1278
00:35:21,300 --> 00:35:22,820
 da se dostupno uspoređuješ.

1279
00:35:22,820 --> 00:35:23,780
 Ši tata je bolji.

1280
00:35:23,780 --> 00:35:25,400
 To je čak bilo neka emisija,

1281
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:25,880
 nevam pojma.

1282
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:28,340
 E, moj tata je bolji od tvog tate,

1283
00:35:28,340 --> 00:35:29,180
 tako je, da, ok.

1284
00:35:29,180 --> 00:35:30,440
 Dakle, da,

1285
00:35:30,440 --> 00:35:32,320
 ali što to znači natjecateljski?

1286
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:32,820
 Kako?

1287
00:35:32,820 --> 00:35:35,420
 S drugim tatama i s drugim muškarcima

1288
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:36,000
 moramo ovo,

1289
00:35:36,000 --> 00:35:36,680
 ko lava ono.

1290
00:35:36,680 --> 00:35:38,840
 Ovaj, dobro,

1291
00:35:38,840 --> 00:35:39,960
 samu, da,

1292
00:35:40,180 --> 00:35:41,160
 ni stio sam nešto reći,

1293
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:41,540
 ali neću.

1294
00:35:41,540 --> 00:35:43,940
 Dakle, ovako.

1295
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:47,340
 Natjesanje i uspoređivanje

1296
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:50,780
 kao nasljedovanje jedni drugih.

1297
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:52,960
 Ne kao temelj za zavisti ili ljubomoru.

1298
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:54,180
 Objasniću.

1299
00:35:54,180 --> 00:35:54,960
 Dakle,

1300
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:57,340
 ako je drugi u nečemu bolji od mene,

1301
00:35:57,340 --> 00:36:00,420
 ako vidim da je neki moj kolega

1302
00:36:00,420 --> 00:36:02,680
 bolji u nekom projektu

1303
00:36:02,680 --> 00:36:05,060
 i imao je neku bolju ideju,

1304
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:07,480
 dakle, neću biti ljubomorani zavida,

1305
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:08,860
 nego, wow, dobra ideja.

1306
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,420
 probat ću ja to kod sebe.

1307
00:36:10,420 --> 00:36:12,540
 Ili, recimo, isto,

1308
00:36:12,540 --> 00:36:16,380
 kada vidite kako neki vaš prijatelj,

1309
00:36:16,380 --> 00:36:17,940
 dakle, su otac,

1310
00:36:17,940 --> 00:36:19,800
 vaš fred i tako dalje,

1311
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:22,140
 koji isto je obiteljski čovjek i tako dalje,

1312
00:36:22,140 --> 00:36:23,360
 rješava neke stvari

1313
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:25,100
 i kako mu ide glatko

1314
00:36:25,100 --> 00:36:27,200
 i kako njegova djeca, ne znam,

1315
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,280
 možda tako ne buče

1316
00:36:28,280 --> 00:36:29,680
 kao što buče tvoja djeca.

1317
00:36:29,680 --> 00:36:31,180
 Dakle, nemo biti, ono,

1318
00:36:31,180 --> 00:36:32,960
 znači, to ti ne treba biti temelj za zavisti

1319
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:33,640
 ili ljubomoru,

1320
00:36:33,640 --> 00:36:35,080
 gledaj, kako imam jednu djecova moja,

1321
00:36:35,080 --> 00:36:35,920
 ne znam,

1322
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,420
 nego, e, kak ti uspjeva?

1323
00:36:37,420 --> 00:36:38,580
 Znači, ono,

1324
00:36:38,580 --> 00:36:41,920
 znači, natjecanje kao nasljedovanje nekoga,

1325
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:44,580
 ne kao temelj za neku, ono,

1326
00:36:44,580 --> 00:36:45,680
 pokazivanje mišića,

1327
00:36:45,680 --> 00:36:46,920
 možemo to tako reći, jel?

1328
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:49,220
 I to se vidi baš na primjeru

1329
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:51,460
 Svetoga Josipa i Boga Otca.

1330
00:36:51,460 --> 00:36:52,540
 Možemo reći,

1331
00:36:52,540 --> 00:36:54,240
 koji je bolji otac, šalju se.

1332
00:36:54,240 --> 00:36:57,120
 Dakle, Sveti Josip,

1333
00:36:57,120 --> 00:36:57,800
 dakle, se,

1334
00:36:57,800 --> 00:36:58,720
 nije ljubomora,

1335
00:36:58,720 --> 00:36:59,460
 gledaj, uzeo mi je,

1336
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:00,640
 pastio mi je brak,

1337
00:37:00,640 --> 00:37:02,240
 ne smije uviša ni taknut,

1338
00:37:02,240 --> 00:37:04,000
 ovo, ono, i tako dalje,

1339
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,640
 nego, znači,

1340
00:37:05,640 --> 00:37:06,840
 idem nasljedovati,

1341
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:09,340
 otvorim se za nasljedovanje Boga Otca,

1342
00:37:09,340 --> 00:37:10,780
 božanskog očinstva.

1343
00:37:10,780 --> 00:37:12,820
 I to je ono što sad

1344
00:37:12,820 --> 00:37:14,060
 utjelovljeni sin treba,

1345
00:37:14,060 --> 00:37:14,660
 je li tako?

1346
00:37:14,660 --> 00:37:15,880
 Dakle, to je ovdje,

1347
00:37:16,200 --> 00:37:18,280
 uzeti nešto od Svetoga Josipa,

1348
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:18,440
 jel?

1349
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:20,700
 E, i sada, na kraju,

1350
00:37:20,700 --> 00:37:23,060
 ćemo zaključiti s ovime.

1351
00:37:23,060 --> 00:37:24,680
 A to je,

1352
00:37:24,680 --> 00:37:26,940
 uvijek moramo zaključiti s nečim,

1353
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:27,940
 možda, negativnim,

1354
00:37:27,940 --> 00:37:31,280
 ali vrlo, možda, isto, isto važno.

1355
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:32,640
 Ja nisamit savjesti,

1356
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:34,440
 ovo bio i meni dok sam ovo radio,

1357
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:36,560
 a možda će biti ispit savjesti i vama.

1358
00:37:36,560 --> 00:37:38,200
 A to je znakovi

1359
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:40,460
 narcisoidnog katoličkog muškarca.

1360
00:37:40,460 --> 00:37:43,360
 Zašto katoličkog muškarca?

1361
00:37:43,360 --> 00:37:44,780
 I to narcisoidnog,

1362
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:46,660
 zato što je, prema istražnosti,

1363
00:37:46,660 --> 00:37:47,400
 statistički,

1364
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,740
 narcisoidnost,

1365
00:37:48,740 --> 00:37:50,680
 u većini su muškarci,

1366
00:37:50,680 --> 00:37:52,080
 oni koji su narcisoidni.

1367
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:53,260
 Žene nemaju to,

1368
00:37:53,260 --> 00:37:54,060
 ima ih žena,

1369
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:57,520
 ali gotovo u nezamjetljivom postotku.

1370
00:37:57,520 --> 00:37:59,820
 Dakle, narcisoidnost je baš ono muška,

1371
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:00,680
 muška bolest,

1372
00:38:00,680 --> 00:38:01,560
 muška patologija,

1373
00:38:01,560 --> 00:38:02,760
 možemo to tako reći, jel?

1374
00:38:03,500 --> 00:38:04,700
 Ok, dobro,

1375
00:38:04,700 --> 00:38:06,120
 ajmo vidjeti sada,

1376
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,580
 na koji na,

1377
00:38:07,580 --> 00:38:08,300
 evo, to bih tio,

1378
00:38:08,300 --> 00:38:09,600
 i to sam podijelio onako,

1379
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:12,180
 od čega se sastoji duhovnost

1380
00:38:12,180 --> 00:38:14,580
 narcisoidnog katolika

1381
00:38:14,580 --> 00:38:17,040
 i kakav je odnos prema bližnjima,

1382
00:38:17,040 --> 00:38:18,400
 prema drugim vjernicima,

1383
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:20,840
 od strane narcisoidnog katolika.

1384
00:38:20,840 --> 00:38:22,560
 Bilo da je član zajednice,

1385
00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:23,960
 bilo da je voditelj zajednice,

1386
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,240
 bilo da je voditelj župe,

1387
00:38:25,240 --> 00:38:26,360
 i tako dalje.

1388
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:26,880
 Ok,

1389
00:38:26,880 --> 00:38:27,640
 dakle,

1390
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,840
 ovo je ispici savesti za sve,

1391
00:38:28,840 --> 00:38:30,140
 koju god ulogu

1392
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:31,100
 i što god,

1393
00:38:31,100 --> 00:38:32,160
 trenutno vršili.

1394
00:38:33,300 --> 00:38:33,660
 Ovako,

1395
00:38:33,660 --> 00:38:35,020
 što je zapravo narcisoidnost?

1396
00:38:35,020 --> 00:38:36,220
 Narcisoidnost je baš one

1397
00:38:36,220 --> 00:38:37,520
 neuspjeli bijeg

1398
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:39,460
 i neuspjelo izlječenje,

1399
00:38:39,460 --> 00:38:40,740
 možemo to tako reći,

1400
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:42,780
 od srama, krivnje i straha.

1401
00:38:42,780 --> 00:38:44,420
 Od one tri uzroka krize

1402
00:38:44,420 --> 00:38:45,180
 uževnosti,

1403
00:38:45,180 --> 00:38:45,760
 možemo reći,

1404
00:38:45,760 --> 00:38:45,940
 jel?

1405
00:38:45,940 --> 00:38:46,640
 Dakle,

1406
00:38:46,640 --> 00:38:48,420
 kada ne zajedno s gospodinom,

1407
00:38:48,420 --> 00:38:49,460
 kao sveti Josip,

1408
00:38:49,460 --> 00:38:50,780
 nego kada ti ideš na sam

1409
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,140
 neko svoje izlječenje,

1410
00:38:52,140 --> 00:38:53,160
 samo izlječenje,

1411
00:38:53,160 --> 00:38:54,240
 ovaj,

1412
00:38:54,240 --> 00:38:56,700
 od vlastitoga osjećaja srama,

1413
00:38:56,700 --> 00:38:58,040
 krivnje i straha.

1414
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:59,300
 Ovako,

1415
00:38:59,300 --> 00:38:59,720
 prvo,

1416
00:38:59,720 --> 00:39:02,460
 po čemu se vidi duhovnost,

1417
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:03,520
 ona intima,

1418
00:39:03,520 --> 00:39:04,860
 unutarnji zapravo život,

1419
00:39:04,860 --> 00:39:07,120
 narcisoidnog katolika.

1420
00:39:07,120 --> 00:39:07,880
 Dakle,

1421
00:39:07,880 --> 00:39:08,980
 narcisoidnog vijenika.

1422
00:39:08,980 --> 00:39:09,800
 Prvo,

1423
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:12,060
 kad ima neke svoje podmisije,

1424
00:39:12,060 --> 00:39:14,100
 sjenovite misije,

1425
00:39:14,100 --> 00:39:15,980
 objasniću što je to.

1426
00:39:15,980 --> 00:39:19,280
 Vi ste u srednjim godinama,

1427
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:20,660
 uvijek te srednje godine.

1428
00:39:20,660 --> 00:39:20,900
 Ok.

1429
00:39:20,900 --> 00:39:21,720
 I sada,

1430
00:39:21,720 --> 00:39:22,300
 znam,

1431
00:39:22,300 --> 00:39:23,380
 bio sam na jednom seminaru,

1432
00:39:23,380 --> 00:39:24,380
 daću možda taj primjer.

1433
00:39:24,380 --> 00:39:25,500
 Bio sam na jednom seminaru,

1434
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:28,480
 isto tako nešto bilo u Rimu

1435
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:30,800
 i bilo nešto o katoličkim muškarcima,

1436
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:31,960
 o vonoj i tako dalje.

1437
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:33,020
 I sad,

1438
00:39:33,020 --> 00:39:34,180
 pozitiv su bile radionice.

1439
00:39:34,180 --> 00:39:35,220
 I,

1440
00:39:35,220 --> 00:39:36,020
 ovaj,

1441
00:39:36,020 --> 00:39:39,660
 mi neki smo bili kao malo voditelji radionica

1442
00:39:39,660 --> 00:39:40,560
 i tako dalje.

1443
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:41,860
 Bilo onako dosta zanimljivo.

1444
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:45,380
 To su neokatokumeni organizirali.

1445
00:39:45,380 --> 00:39:46,820
 Ovaj,

1446
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:47,340
 i sad,

1447
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:48,460
 ovako smo bili u krugu

1448
00:39:48,460 --> 00:39:49,440
 i sad,

1449
00:39:49,440 --> 00:39:51,680
 svako je pričao neke svoje,

1450
00:39:51,680 --> 00:39:52,100
 ne znam,

1451
00:39:52,100 --> 00:39:53,600
 gdje vidi svoju krizu,

1452
00:39:53,600 --> 00:39:55,200
 trenutno o vonoj i tako dalje.

1453
00:39:55,660 --> 00:39:55,940
 I sad,

1454
00:39:55,940 --> 00:39:58,340
 i jedan je onako isto ustao,

1455
00:39:58,340 --> 00:39:58,780
 to je ono,

1456
00:39:58,780 --> 00:39:59,160
 kono,

1457
00:39:59,160 --> 00:39:59,660
 ej, ej,

1458
00:39:59,660 --> 00:39:59,960
 znate,

1459
00:39:59,960 --> 00:40:01,000
 ali ono mi je alkoholičari,

1460
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:02,080
 tako je to izgledalo malo.

1461
00:40:02,080 --> 00:40:03,660
 I rekao je,

1462
00:40:03,660 --> 00:40:06,260
 gotovo svaku večer,

1463
00:40:06,260 --> 00:40:09,900
 kada moja žena i moja djeca odu spavati,

1464
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:11,540
 pošaljem ih,

1465
00:40:11,540 --> 00:40:13,100
 baš se ono izrazio,

1466
00:40:13,100 --> 00:40:13,300
 jel?

1467
00:40:13,300 --> 00:40:14,600
 Ovaj,

1468
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:17,340
 i ja sam sam za računalom

1469
00:40:17,340 --> 00:40:19,180
 i zabavljam se.

1470
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:21,080
 Tako je rekao.

1471
00:40:21,080 --> 00:40:21,400
 Bila,

1472
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:21,840
 ok,

1473
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:22,960
 malo previše informacija.

1474
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:25,100
 Ali,

1475
00:40:25,100 --> 00:40:26,200
 to je njegova podmisija.

1476
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,440
 Znači,

1477
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:29,040
 bijega od odgovornosti,

1478
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:31,380
 on je svoje spremio spavati i tako dalje,

1479
00:40:31,380 --> 00:40:33,060
 i on ima svoju podmisiju.

1480
00:40:33,060 --> 00:40:33,460
 To je to.

1481
00:40:33,460 --> 00:40:35,360
 Svaku večer radi to i to.

1482
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:36,160
 Jel?

1483
00:40:36,160 --> 00:40:38,860
 On to nije rekao zato što se ti me hvali,

1484
00:40:38,860 --> 00:40:40,800
 nego podijelio, dakle,

1485
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:41,620
 tu svoju muku.

1486
00:40:41,620 --> 00:40:41,900
 Jel?

1487
00:40:41,900 --> 00:40:46,260
 Što se može dovesti do nekih tih,

1488
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:46,640
 ajmo reći,

1489
00:40:46,640 --> 00:40:47,400
 sjenovitih,

1490
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:48,560
 nekih podmisija?

1491
00:40:48,560 --> 00:40:48,920
 Dakle,

1492
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:50,800
 tvoja misija je

1493
00:40:50,800 --> 00:40:52,180
 biti otac,

1494
00:40:52,180 --> 00:40:53,660
 biti svečenik ovo ono.

1495
00:40:53,660 --> 00:40:54,220
 Dakle,

1496
00:40:54,220 --> 00:40:55,880
 ajmo reći dvostruki život.

1497
00:40:55,880 --> 00:40:57,500
 Mi često znamo reći,

1498
00:40:57,500 --> 00:41:00,180
 govoriti o svečeničkim dvostrukim životima.

1499
00:41:00,180 --> 00:41:00,600
 Jel?

1500
00:41:00,600 --> 00:41:01,260
 Dopija vita,

1501
00:41:01,260 --> 00:41:02,400
 kako talijani kažu.

1502
00:41:02,400 --> 00:41:03,100
 Međutim,

1503
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:05,040
 naravno da postoji dvostruki život

1504
00:41:05,040 --> 00:41:05,680
 jednog oca,

1505
00:41:05,680 --> 00:41:06,160
 nažalost,

1506
00:41:06,160 --> 00:41:07,000
 može postojati,

1507
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:07,840
 jednog muškarca,

1508
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:08,400
 jednog dečka,

1509
00:41:08,460 --> 00:41:09,740
 jednog zaručnika i tako dalje.

1510
00:41:09,740 --> 00:41:13,020
 Upravo ona dugotraja na pasivnost,

1511
00:41:13,020 --> 00:41:14,000
 o kojoj sam na početku,

1512
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,160
 kada uđete u brak,

1513
00:41:15,160 --> 00:41:17,440
 zapravo o čemu sam govorio,

1514
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:18,760
 ona dugotraja na pasivnost.

1515
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:19,380
 Dakle,

1516
00:41:19,380 --> 00:41:20,760
 ona je jednostatak samo kontrole

1517
00:41:20,760 --> 00:41:22,060
 i onda pod izlikom

1518
00:41:22,060 --> 00:41:23,540
 ja sam tolerantan muž,

1519
00:41:23,540 --> 00:41:25,040
 pa svoje ženi sve prepuštam,

1520
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:26,660
 nisak si lijen i pasivan si.

1521
00:41:26,660 --> 00:41:28,180
 Dakle,

1522
00:41:28,180 --> 00:41:29,920
 upravo ta dugotraja na pasivnost

1523
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:31,560
 i davanje kontrole drugima

1524
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:33,820
 dovodi do podmisija.

1525
00:41:33,820 --> 00:41:34,240
 Znači,

1526
00:41:34,240 --> 00:41:35,620
 izdaja odgovornosti.

1527
00:41:35,620 --> 00:41:36,280
 I kažem,

1528
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:37,860
 najčešće u srednjim godinama.

1529
00:41:37,860 --> 00:41:38,060
 Dakle,

1530
00:41:38,060 --> 00:41:38,600
 to je prvo.

1531
00:41:38,600 --> 00:41:39,720
 To je prvo.

1532
00:41:39,720 --> 00:41:40,360
 Dakle,

1533
00:41:40,360 --> 00:41:41,940
 prva oznaka u intimi

1534
00:41:41,940 --> 00:41:43,440
 narcisovnog katolika je to,

1535
00:41:43,440 --> 00:41:44,920
 ima neke svoje podmisije,

1536
00:41:44,920 --> 00:41:46,500
 nešto svoje sa strane.

1537
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:49,120
 Ono što sam rekao,

1538
00:41:49,120 --> 00:41:49,460
 recimo,

1539
00:41:49,460 --> 00:41:51,420
 isto kao svećenik,

1540
00:41:51,420 --> 00:41:52,580
 ima neku svoju podmisiju.

1541
00:41:52,580 --> 00:41:52,940
 Ja sam,

1542
00:41:52,940 --> 00:41:53,460
 na primjer,

1543
00:41:53,460 --> 00:41:55,200
 ne znam,

1544
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:56,820
 ovdje sam župnik i tako dalje,

1545
00:41:57,340 --> 00:41:58,240
 ali isto vremeno,

1546
00:41:58,240 --> 00:41:59,120
 idem negdje,

1547
00:41:59,120 --> 00:41:59,760
 ne znam,

1548
00:41:59,760 --> 00:42:00,620
 drugdje,

1549
00:42:00,620 --> 00:42:02,500
 na susrete neke,

1550
00:42:02,500 --> 00:42:04,680
 nije to loše ić na susret neke zajednice,

1551
00:42:04,680 --> 00:42:08,360
 ali ako u to vrijeme bi trebao imati nešto drugo ovdje,

1552
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:09,680
 onda je tu problem.

1553
00:42:09,680 --> 00:42:10,880
 Drugo,

1554
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:14,980
 je preuzetno doživljavanje božanske providnosti.

1555
00:42:14,980 --> 00:42:15,840
 Dakle,

1556
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:17,700
 to je baš ono narcisojna duhovnost.

1557
00:42:17,700 --> 00:42:18,140
 Dakle,

1558
00:42:18,140 --> 00:42:20,680
 ono preuzetno doživljavanje božanske providnosti.

1559
00:42:20,680 --> 00:42:21,060
 Ja,

1560
00:42:21,060 --> 00:42:22,760
 pa kome će Bog pomoći ako na meni?

1561
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:23,280
 Pa vidi me.

1562
00:42:23,880 --> 00:42:24,180
 Dakle,

1563
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:26,500
 Bog je tu uvijek meni na raspolaganju.

1564
00:42:26,500 --> 00:42:27,580
 Ja sam izabran,

1565
00:42:27,580 --> 00:42:28,980
 ja sam neodoljiv i tako dalje.

1566
00:42:28,980 --> 00:42:30,060
 Dakle,

1567
00:42:30,060 --> 00:42:31,100
 to,

1568
00:42:31,100 --> 00:42:33,960
 meni Bog mora pomoći.

1569
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:34,920
 Ali to je baš ono,

1570
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:36,320
 totalno uvjerenje.

1571
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:38,140
 Ne ono povjerenje u božu,

1572
00:42:38,140 --> 00:42:40,020
 nego baš ono preuzetno,

1573
00:42:40,020 --> 00:42:42,080
 gotovo onako imperativno.

1574
00:42:42,080 --> 00:42:43,340
 Bog mi mora pomoći.

1575
00:42:43,340 --> 00:42:44,540
 Kome će drugom ako ne meni?

1576
00:42:44,540 --> 00:42:46,040
 I treće,

1577
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:47,460
 što odlika,

1578
00:42:47,460 --> 00:42:50,420
 odnosno negativnost ove duhovnosti narcisojne,

1579
00:42:50,420 --> 00:42:51,300
 je,

1580
00:42:51,300 --> 00:42:53,840
 povezano je sa onim što ćemo

1581
00:42:53,840 --> 00:42:55,280
 sada u odnosu prema drugima,

1582
00:42:55,280 --> 00:42:57,780
 a to je s obzirom na pitanje autoriteta.

1583
00:42:57,780 --> 00:42:58,800
 Dakle,

1584
00:42:58,800 --> 00:43:02,400
 vlastiti autoritet,

1585
00:43:02,400 --> 00:43:04,340
 znači moj autoritet,

1586
00:43:04,340 --> 00:43:07,360
 narcisoidnog katolika,

1587
00:43:07,360 --> 00:43:10,060
 je temeljen na podkopavanju tuđeg autoriteta.

1588
00:43:10,060 --> 00:43:11,020
 Dakle,

1589
00:43:11,020 --> 00:43:13,720
 ja neću na temeljiti svoj autoritet

1590
00:43:13,720 --> 00:43:15,980
 na tome da vam budem na usluzi,

1591
00:43:15,980 --> 00:43:17,940
 da pokažem svoje kvalitete,

1592
00:43:17,940 --> 00:43:19,740
 da zaista ono,

1593
00:43:19,740 --> 00:43:21,760
 zajedno gradimo nešto i tako dalje,

1594
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:22,200
 nego ne.

1595
00:43:22,200 --> 00:43:24,020
 Netko koji je bio ili prije,

1596
00:43:24,020 --> 00:43:25,400
 ili predprije,

1597
00:43:25,400 --> 00:43:26,140
 ili ne znam kada,

1598
00:43:26,140 --> 00:43:28,200
 ja ću podkopavati njegov autoriteti

1599
00:43:28,200 --> 00:43:29,740
 na temelju toga kad podkopam,

1600
00:43:29,740 --> 00:43:30,880
 ja sta sam.

1601
00:43:30,880 --> 00:43:33,460
 Vidjet ćemo što kad mu uspije,

1602
00:43:33,460 --> 00:43:34,520
 a što kad mu ne uspije,

1603
00:43:34,520 --> 00:43:35,180
 što se događa,

1604
00:43:35,180 --> 00:43:36,160
 što se onda pretvara.

1605
00:43:36,700 --> 00:43:40,240
 Ugled gradim na umalovažavanju autoriteta.

1606
00:43:40,240 --> 00:43:41,880
 Bilo župnik biskupovog,

1607
00:43:41,880 --> 00:43:45,100
 bilo voditelj neke zajednice župnikovog,

1608
00:43:45,100 --> 00:43:46,640
 bilo član neke zajednice,

1609
00:43:46,640 --> 00:43:48,340
 podkopava voditelja zajednice.

1610
00:43:48,340 --> 00:43:50,080
 Kako god hoćete hierarhijski.

1611
00:43:50,660 --> 00:43:52,480
 Dakle, riječ je o narcisojnoj osobi.

1612
00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:53,740
 E sada,

1613
00:43:53,740 --> 00:43:56,500
 ako joj to uspije,

1614
00:43:56,500 --> 00:43:58,080
 podkopava autoritet,

1615
00:43:58,080 --> 00:43:59,000
 i on se pokaže,

1616
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:01,160
 ili ona kao neki sad novi autoritet,

1617
00:44:01,160 --> 00:44:03,400
 onda dolazi do mesijanskog kompleksa.

1618
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:05,160
 Ako ne uspije,

1619
00:44:05,160 --> 00:44:07,320
 onda dolazi do kompleksa mučeništva.

1620
00:44:07,320 --> 00:44:08,920
 Što je mesijanski kompleks?

1621
00:44:08,920 --> 00:44:12,180
 Dakle, ja sam dar svoje obitelji,

1622
00:44:12,180 --> 00:44:13,920
 svoje župi, svoje zajednice.

1623
00:44:13,920 --> 00:44:16,480
 Meni sa jednog slušajer sam ja i zabran.

1624
00:44:16,480 --> 00:44:20,200
 Zato su moje odluke jedine odraz Božje volje.

1625
00:44:20,200 --> 00:44:21,720
 Jel?

1626
00:44:21,720 --> 00:44:24,280
 Dakle, i to ovako.

1627
00:44:24,280 --> 00:44:27,560
 To baš ono nastaje nekim potisnutim osjećajima

1628
00:44:27,560 --> 00:44:30,800
 ili podkopavanjem i vlastite muškosti prije svega.

1629
00:44:30,800 --> 00:44:32,840
 Recimo, kako se izražava?

1630
00:44:32,840 --> 00:44:39,020
 Ako se potisnuta muškost želi, dakle, ispoljeti.

1631
00:44:39,020 --> 00:44:41,420
 Ono, eksplozija, onda je agresivan.

1632
00:44:41,420 --> 00:44:43,980
 Znači, narcisoidost postaje agresija.

1633
00:44:43,980 --> 00:44:47,580
 A agresija je upravo to, potisnuta muškost.

1634
00:44:47,580 --> 00:44:49,420
 Cijelo vrijeme je bila zaključavana,

1635
00:44:49,420 --> 00:44:50,800
 cijelo vrijeme je ono potkopavana,

1636
00:44:50,800 --> 00:44:52,640
 cijelo vrijeme je ovo ono i pukosan.

1637
00:44:52,640 --> 00:44:56,700
 A s druge strane, ako potisnuta muškost

1638
00:44:56,700 --> 00:44:59,380
 ne da eksplodira, nego implodira, možemo reći.

1639
00:44:59,380 --> 00:45:00,880
 Onak, eksplodira iznutra,

1640
00:45:00,880 --> 00:45:02,440
 onda pada u depresiju.

1641
00:45:02,840 --> 00:45:03,800
 Onda je depresivan.

1642
00:45:03,800 --> 00:45:06,980
 Ali negdje je puklo, bilo vani, to je agresija,

1643
00:45:06,980 --> 00:45:08,440
 bilo unutra, depresija.

1644
00:45:08,440 --> 00:45:11,820
 Ok, a kompleks mučeništva,

1645
00:45:11,820 --> 00:45:15,420
 dakle, ako ne uspije srušiti autoritet.

1646
00:45:15,420 --> 00:45:19,420
 Dakle, uvijek, pogledaj, vi njega slušate,

1647
00:45:19,420 --> 00:45:20,860
 pogledaj što mi je učinio,

1648
00:45:20,860 --> 00:45:23,060
 dakle, taj je komplek žrtve i tako dalje.

1649
00:45:23,140 --> 00:45:24,700
 onda pokušava na taj način.

1650
00:45:24,700 --> 00:45:28,260
 Zapravo, opravdati ono kad je nekoga prokazao.

1651
00:45:28,260 --> 00:45:31,040
 Onda, znači to je to, vlastne autoritete,

1652
00:45:31,040 --> 00:45:33,700
 menja na potkopavanju tuđeg autoriteta.

1653
00:45:33,700 --> 00:45:36,140
 Recimo, objasnio sam aktivno,

1654
00:45:36,140 --> 00:45:38,780
 a pogledajte kako pasivno se može potkopavati.

1655
00:45:39,700 --> 00:45:43,540
 Na primjer, kada pita za savjet autoritet,

1656
00:45:43,540 --> 00:45:44,940
 ali to ne odradi.

1657
00:45:44,940 --> 00:45:48,900
 Dakle, to je pasivno potkopavanje.

1658
00:45:48,900 --> 00:45:50,140
 Na primjer, ok,

1659
00:45:50,140 --> 00:45:53,600
 znači, ono aktivno je baš javno govore

1660
00:45:53,600 --> 00:45:54,720
 protiv nekoga ovo ono.

1661
00:45:54,720 --> 00:45:56,380
 A pasivno daću taj primjer.

1662
00:45:56,380 --> 00:45:58,880
 Na primjer, autoritet pita za neki savjet,

1663
00:45:58,880 --> 00:46:01,100
 ja pitam autoritet za neki savjet,

1664
00:46:01,100 --> 00:46:02,540
 ali ga neću slušati.

1665
00:46:02,540 --> 00:46:04,140
 Nego, što ću još napraviti?

1666
00:46:04,140 --> 00:46:09,020
 Dakle, taj savjet i tu zapovjed,

1667
00:46:09,140 --> 00:46:11,080
 taj nalog koji mi je dao moj autoritet,

1668
00:46:11,080 --> 00:46:12,700
 ja ću komentirati s drugima.

1669
00:46:12,700 --> 00:46:15,800
 Znači, ako reći ću kako ja mislim

1670
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:16,820
 da to nije bilo dobro,

1671
00:46:16,820 --> 00:46:19,480
 ja mi znači da taj savjet nije bio na mojoj izgranju,

1672
00:46:19,480 --> 00:46:21,740
 pa reci to autoritetu koji ti je dao savjet.

1673
00:46:21,740 --> 00:46:23,100
 Zašto imaš svoj krug ljudi

1674
00:46:23,100 --> 00:46:23,920
 s kojim to moraš...

1675
00:46:23,920 --> 00:46:26,040
 Dakle, to je pasivno potkopavanje autoriteta.

1676
00:46:26,040 --> 00:46:29,420
 Sveti Josip nema problema s time.

1677
00:46:29,420 --> 00:46:30,740
 Gledajte jednu stvar.

1678
00:46:30,740 --> 00:46:33,160
 Dakle, Sveti Josip je kraljevske časti.

1679
00:46:33,160 --> 00:46:35,780
 I on nema potkopavanje autoriteta

1680
00:46:35,780 --> 00:46:38,080
 u smislu, on ide u hram, sluša zakon,

1681
00:46:38,080 --> 00:46:39,740
 sluša farizeje.

1682
00:46:39,740 --> 00:46:41,620
 On je mogao reći, ovo je Sid Boži,

1683
00:46:41,620 --> 00:46:42,960
 meni je došao Anđeo Gospodnji.

1684
00:46:42,960 --> 00:46:45,180
 Što ćemo mi sada se podlagati

1685
00:46:45,180 --> 00:46:46,740
 nekom starom zakonu židovskom?

1686
00:46:47,120 --> 00:46:48,660
 Nije ću ja ću njega ubriti za tu hramu.

1687
00:46:48,660 --> 00:46:50,120
 Meni je došao Anđeo Gospodnji,

1688
00:46:50,120 --> 00:46:51,180
 to je sigurno Sid Boži.

1689
00:46:51,180 --> 00:46:52,880
 Ili, na primjer,

1690
00:46:52,880 --> 00:46:54,520
 car Augusta ili kralj Herod.

1691
00:46:54,520 --> 00:46:56,940
 Ne ma nikakve riječi protiv njih.

1692
00:46:56,940 --> 00:46:58,520
 On se podlaže

1693
00:46:58,520 --> 00:47:00,300
 tadašnjim autoritetu.

1694
00:47:00,300 --> 00:47:02,160
 Propisu cara Augusta

1695
00:47:02,160 --> 00:47:03,840
 i kralju Herodu.

1696
00:47:03,840 --> 00:47:04,800
 Isto tako.

1697
00:47:04,800 --> 00:47:05,180
 Jel?

1698
00:47:05,180 --> 00:47:07,220
 Kakav god bi autoritet,

1699
00:47:07,220 --> 00:47:09,460
 taj autoritet je tako da,

1700
00:47:09,460 --> 00:47:10,760
 ne trebaš se s njime složiti,

1701
00:47:10,760 --> 00:47:12,500
 ali nemoj ga, dakle,

1702
00:47:12,500 --> 00:47:14,640
 aktivno ili pasivno potkopavati.

1703
00:47:14,640 --> 00:47:15,440
 Dakle, to vidimo.

1704
00:47:15,440 --> 00:47:16,700
 Jer to jednače, ono,

1705
00:47:16,700 --> 00:47:17,700
 baš narcisoidno.

1706
00:47:17,700 --> 00:47:18,040
 Ok.

1707
00:47:18,040 --> 00:47:20,080
 Dakle, i ono,

1708
00:47:20,080 --> 00:47:21,260
 kada dobiveni savjet,

1709
00:47:21,260 --> 00:47:23,180
 okrećeš protiv samog autoriteta.

1710
00:47:23,180 --> 00:47:24,680
 To je ona igra.

1711
00:47:24,680 --> 00:47:26,180
 Dakle, a zašto?

1712
00:47:26,180 --> 00:47:28,020
 Pa to ste mi vi savjetovali tako.

1713
00:47:28,020 --> 00:47:29,780
 Što je, u čemu je sad problem?

1714
00:47:29,780 --> 00:47:30,520
 Ok.

1715
00:47:30,520 --> 00:47:33,020
 Onda, imamo još dvije stvari.

1716
00:47:33,020 --> 00:47:34,540
 Lažna podiznost.

1717
00:47:34,540 --> 00:47:36,620
 To smo čuvali sto puta.

1718
00:47:36,620 --> 00:47:38,220
 Konkretno kako izgleda

1719
00:47:38,220 --> 00:47:39,460
 muška lažna podiznost?

1720
00:47:39,460 --> 00:47:41,080
 Baš ono, muška lažna podiznost.

1721
00:47:41,080 --> 00:47:42,580
 Dakle, ovako.

1722
00:47:44,640 --> 00:47:46,700
 Lažna podiznost,

1723
00:47:46,700 --> 00:47:48,400
 prije svega što je podiznost?

1724
00:47:48,400 --> 00:47:49,700
 Podiznost je, dakle,

1725
00:47:49,700 --> 00:47:51,760
 govoriti ili malo

1726
00:47:51,760 --> 00:47:53,240
 ili uopće ne govoriti o sebi.

1727
00:47:53,240 --> 00:47:54,460
 To je podiznost.

1728
00:47:54,460 --> 00:47:55,460
 Tu je sveti osip,

1729
00:47:55,460 --> 00:47:56,560
 naravno, prvi pretljači,

1730
00:47:56,560 --> 00:47:57,020
 jel' tako?

1731
00:47:57,020 --> 00:47:58,360
 Dakle, to je podiznost.

1732
00:47:58,360 --> 00:48:00,700
 Govoriti o sebi malo,

1733
00:48:00,700 --> 00:48:01,880
 kada mi se nešto pita,

1734
00:48:01,880 --> 00:48:03,520
 ili uopće ne govoriti o sebi.

1735
00:48:04,220 --> 00:48:05,720
 Kako onda izgleda lažna podiznost?

1736
00:48:05,720 --> 00:48:08,260
 Ako dosta govori o sebi,

1737
00:48:08,260 --> 00:48:09,860
 čak i o ne negativnosti,

1738
00:48:09,860 --> 00:48:11,380
 najčešće negativnosti,

1739
00:48:11,380 --> 00:48:12,280
 ali govoriš o sebi.

1740
00:48:12,280 --> 00:48:15,380
 Dakle, dijeli svoju intimu,

1741
00:48:15,380 --> 00:48:17,400
 svi živi znaju kakvih je problema

1742
00:48:17,400 --> 00:48:19,200
 ima s mamom, ima s tatom,

1743
00:48:19,200 --> 00:48:20,720
 ne samo duhovnik te osobe,

1744
00:48:20,720 --> 00:48:22,040
 nego svi, svi živi.

1745
00:48:23,440 --> 00:48:24,300
 svoje rane,

1746
00:48:24,300 --> 00:48:26,440
 razglavio i objašnjava s drugima

1747
00:48:26,440 --> 00:48:27,640
 ili s mnogima.

1748
00:48:27,640 --> 00:48:29,400
 Puno govori o svom životu

1749
00:48:29,400 --> 00:48:30,780
 prije obraćenja, na primjer.

1750
00:48:30,780 --> 00:48:31,900
 Jako voli svoj život.

1751
00:48:31,900 --> 00:48:33,360
 Jako govori pričati o sebi,

1752
00:48:33,360 --> 00:48:35,440
 kakav sam ja bio kao stari čovjek,

1753
00:48:35,440 --> 00:48:36,940
 kakav sam ja bio u prošlom.

1754
00:48:36,940 --> 00:48:39,300
 Jako, mislim, jedno je svijedočiti

1755
00:48:39,300 --> 00:48:41,020
 jedan put kad mi se nešto pita.

1756
00:48:41,020 --> 00:48:42,120
 Govoriti cijelo vrijeme,

1757
00:48:42,120 --> 00:48:43,720
 to je već malo narcisoidno,

1758
00:48:43,720 --> 00:48:45,900
 ta fiksacija na stari,

1759
00:48:45,900 --> 00:48:47,080
 prošli, grešli život.

1760
00:48:47,080 --> 00:48:49,620
 Mnogo se ponižava,

1761
00:48:49,620 --> 00:48:51,280
 baš ono, ponižavanje,

1762
00:48:51,920 --> 00:48:53,960
 ili aktivno se skriva

1763
00:48:53,960 --> 00:48:55,540
 iza drugih članova.

1764
00:48:55,540 --> 00:48:56,500
 Možemo to tako reći.

