1894
00:52:23,300 --> 00:52:24,960
 na osobnim doživljajima

1895
00:52:24,960 --> 00:52:27,480
 ulomaka Svetoga pisma

1896
00:52:27,480 --> 00:52:28,900
 koje stiču Svetoga Josipa.

1897
00:52:29,320 --> 00:52:29,940
 Ali naravno,

1898
00:52:29,940 --> 00:52:31,180
