1926
00:53:05,520 --> 00:53:08,460
 obiteljskih, privatnih,

1927
00:53:08,460 --> 00:53:09,220
 možemo reći.

1928
00:53:09,220 --> 00:53:10,000
 Dakle,

1929
00:53:10,000 --> 00:53:11,880
 nešto što se tiče

