00:54:49,560 --> 00:54:52,100
 Bilo s obzirom na vlastni identitet,

1996
00:54:52,100 --> 00:54:54,140
 bilo s obzirom na ovo što su napravili,

1997
00:54:54,140 --> 00:54:55,340
